%^BOLD%^-=%^YELLOW%^Creation Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Drawing upon the powers of conjuration, the creation domain is quite useful, producing everything from common goods to wards of protection that are difficult to bypass. In addition, the domain may also create a particularly powerful spell to harm foes.

Clerics with the Creation Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +1 bonus to caster level when casting conjuration school spells.

The creation domain contains the following spells:

Mending, Stinking Cloud, Secret Chest, Sticks Into Snakes, Acid Fog

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kismet

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
